Class DomainTransferResponse

    • com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.se.Response

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class DomainTransferResponse
extends TransferResponse
    Use this to access domain object transfer information as provided in an EPP domain transfer response compliant with RFC5730 and RFC5731. Such a service element is sent by a compliant EPP server in response to a valid domain transfer command, implemented by a subclass of the DomainTransferCommand class.
    See Also:
    DomainTransferCommand, DomainTransferRequestCommand, DomainTransferApproveCommand, DomainTransferCancelCommand, DomainTransferRejectCommand, DomainTransferQueryCommand, Serialized Form
